node.title: Baby with possible 'non-accidental' injuries dies at Starship
node.description: The 10-month-old boy had injuries believed to be "non-accidental", police said on Friday.
node.content: ["A critically injured baby taken to Starship Hospital on Wednesday has died, prompting a homicide investigation.", "The 10-month-old boy had injuries believed to be \"non-accidental\", police said on Friday.", "He has since died. A post mortem will take place on Saturday.", "\"As such, the investigation has now been upgraded to a homicide inquiry,\" Det Insp Aaron Proctor said.", "\"Police inquiries are continuing, and any further updates will be provided when able.\"", "No one had been arrested as of Friday.\u00a0", "\u00a0"]
